OL,3,CNicola Sturgeon: My arrest was
OL,4,C'horrific' and part of me 'closed down'
OL,6,FScotland's former first minister
OL,7,FNicola Sturgeon has described the day
OL,8,Fshe was arrested as "horrific" and
OL,9,F"the worst day of her life."
OL,11,FIn an exclusive interview with ITV
OL,12,FNews, ahead of the release of her
OL,13,Fmemoir, Frankly, Sturgeon talks about
OL,14,Fthe day of her arrest, telling Julie
OL,15,FEtchingham, "I think a part of me just
OL,16,Fclosed down."
OL,18,FShe also described the "horror, upset
OL,19,Fand shame" of her husband's arrest in
OL,20,FApril 2023.
