OL,3,CNicola Sturgeon: My arrest was
OL,4,C'horrific' and part of me 'closed down'
OL,6,FIn a wide-ranging and frank
OL,7,Fdiscussion, the former first minister
OL,8,Falso expressed regret in her handling
OL,9,Fof transgender legislation during her
OL,10,Ftime in office, admitting she should
OL,11,Fhave "paused" the legislation when the
OL,12,Fdebate became polarised.
OL,14,FShe writes in her book, "I have never
OL,15,Fconsidered sexuality, my own included,
OL,16,Fto be binary," adding that she was
OL,17,F"enjoying being her own person for a
OL,18,Fwhile".
