OL,3,CNicola Sturgeon: My arrest was
OL,4,C'horrific' and part of me 'closed down'
OL,6,FOver the past few years, the Scottish
OL,7,FNational Party has been embroiled in a
OL,8,Ffinancial scandal.
OL,10,FThis resulted in a police
OL,11,Finvestigation examining criminal
OL,12,Fwrongdoing around the SNP's finances,
OL,13,Fnamed Operation Branchform. On April 5
OL,14,F2023, Peter Murrell, Sturgeon's then
OL,15,Fhusband and SNP chief executive, was
OL,16,Farrested by Police Scotland at the
OL,17,Fcouple's Glasgow home in connection
OL,18,Fwith Operation Branchform.
