OL,3,CNicola Sturgeon: My arrest was
OL,4,C'horrific' and part of me 'closed down'
OL,6,FNicola Sturgeon was herself arrested
OL,7,Fon June 11 in connection with the same
OL,8,Finvestigation.
OL,10,FShe would later be cleared of all
OL,11,Fcharges, but her husband, from whom
OL,12,Fshe's now separated, would go on to be
OL,13,Fcharged with embezzlement, events she
OL,14,Fdescribed as "horrific".
OL,16,FThe former first minister told ITV
OL,17,FNews' Julie Etchingham that she had
OL,18,F"blocked out" the details of her
OL,19,Fhusband's arrest at their family home.
