OL,3,CNicola Sturgeon: My arrest was
OL,4,C'horrific' and part of me 'closed down'
OL,6,FSturgeon said she still found it
OL,7,Fdifficult to articulate how she felt
OL,8,Fseeing her husband arrested.
OL,10,F"It wasn't until I got to mum and
OL,11,Fdad's that I saw the pictures of my
OL,12,Fhouse looking like a murder scene,
OL,13,Feffectively," she said.
OL,15,F"I had this sense of horror, upset,
OL,16,Fand the kind of shame of it all."
OL,18,F"I think part of me just closed down,"
OL,19,Fshe said.
