OL,11,FHer time in office was not without its
OL,12,Fshare of difficulties, either.
OL,14,FTowards the end of Sturgeon's tenure,
OL,15,Fshe introduced legislation aimed at
OL,16,Fmaking it easier for transgender
OL,17,Fpeople to self-identify their gender,
OL,18,Fwithout a medical diagnosis.
