OL,4,C'horrific' and part of me 'closed down'
OL,6,FBut the Gender Recognition Reform
OL,7,F(Scotland) Bill went on to spark a
OL,8,F"divisive" and at times "toxic" debate
OL,9,Fover gender identity, eventually
OL,10,Fleading to April's Supreme Court
OL,11,Fruling against the Scottish government
OL,12,Fon the issue.
OL,14,FNicola Sturgeon tells ITV News she
OL,15,Fdidn't engage as much as she should
OL,16,Fhave with concerns around the gender
OL,17,Freform bill
