OL,3,CNicola Sturgeon: My arrest was
OL,4,C'horrific' and part of me 'closed down'
OL,6,FITV News asked the former FM how she
OL,7,Ffelt about the fact that the fallout
OL,8,Fof the debate around her reforms may
OL,9,Fhave made things worse for the lives
OL,10,Fof transgender people across the UK.
OL,12,F"When this was first mooted, it was
OL,13,Fnot the divisive, toxic, controversial
OL,14,Fissue it became," explained Sturgeon.
OL,16,FReflecting on the shape the debate
OL,17,Ftook, however, she signalled some
OL,18,Fregret, admitting she should have
OL,19,F"taken a step back" and "paused" the
OL,20,Flegislation.
