OL,3,CNicola Sturgeon: My arrest was
OL,4,C'horrific' and part of me 'closed down'
OL,6,FExpanding, she described it to ITV
OL,7,FNews as "just (her) view of the world,
OL,8,Fand life, and the way people are."
OL,10,FShe went on to clarify, "If you're
OL,11,Fabout to ask me, 'Am I making some big
OL,12,Frevelation?' No. 'Am I putting labels
OL,13,Fon myself?' No, I'm just... that's how
OL,14,FI see the world."
OL,16,FWhilst the former first minister
OL,17,Fdidn't rule out the possibility of a
OL,18,Frelationship with a woman, she added:
OL,19,F"Look, I'm just out of a marriage, so
OL,20,FI'm not rushing into a relationship
OL,21,Fwith anyone anytime soon.
